  "description": {
    "lang": "eng",
    "value": "Path traversal for some Intel(R) Extension for Transformers software before version 1.5 may allow an authenticated user to potentially enable escalation of privilege via local access.\n\nReason for inclusion in AVID: CVE-2024-21799 describes a path traversal vulnerability in Intel Extension for Transformers software before version 1.5, enabling local privilege escalation. The affected component is a software library used in AI pipelines, thus a software supply chain issue for general-purpose AI systems. It is a security vulnerability with documented references (NVD, Intel advisory)."
  },
